      <title>美国零售额上升，失业救济申请下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-15/us-retail-sales-rise-jobless-claims-fall-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[数据显示，美国 7 月份零售额增长超过预期，整体呈上升趋势。另一份报告显示，失业救济申请降至 7 月初以来的最低水平。受此消息推动，股市上涨。彭博社的 Michael McKee 报道。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-15/us-retail-sales-rise-jobless-claims-fall-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 13:29:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储可以加快利率正常化进程：摩根大通的张</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-15/fed-can-speed-up-rate-normalization-jpmorgan-s-chang-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根大通全球研究主管 Joyce Chang 表示，未来六个月的路径很清晰，她解释了为什么美联储应该在年底前实施 100 个基点的宽松政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-15/fed-can-speed-up-rate-normalization-jpmorgan-s-chang-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 13:16:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>康斯坦：股市处于软着陆状态</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-15/equities-comfortable-in-soft-landing-position-konstam-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞穗宏观策略主管多米尼克·康斯塔姆 (Dominic Konstam) 表示，债券市场和股票市场“在某种程度上处于相同的软着陆位置”，但这两个市场都不适合美联储大幅降息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-15/equities-comfortable-in-soft-landing-position-konstam-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 13:09:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>数据排除大幅降息可能性，国债收益率大幅上升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-15/treasury-yields-rise-sharply-as-data-rules-out-big-rate-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国经济数据强劲，促使交易员降低对美联储今年大幅降息的预期，随后美国国债收益率飙升。]]></description>
